Returns a urllib3 connection for the given URL. This should not be called from user code, and is only exposed for use when subclassing the HTTPAdapter <requests.adapters.HTTPAdapter>.

Returns a dictionary of the headers to add to any request sent through a proxy. This works with urllib3 magic to ensure that they are correctly sent to the proxy, rather than in a tunnelled request if CONNECT is being used.  This should not be called from user code, and is only exposed for use when subclassing the HTTPAdapter <requests.adapters.HTTPAdapter>.
